s and close the shielding boxes. The two-colored LED of DUTs which could label PASS or FAIL during th<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">e test process is connected to LED interface to enable operator to know the test outcome of every devices.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\">UT-804 can expand by connecting with other UT-804, which means customers could expand the function of UT-804 from 1 to 4 to 1 to 16.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><img src=\"/Upload/ueditor/2018-03-02/1519971151.jpg\" title=\"1519971151.jpg\" alt=\"UT-804.jpg\"/></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Convenient user interface</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The DLL of UT-804 module provides initialization, switching of port and LED to make it easier to fit the software. The DLL can support serial control of 4 modules. With combiner, user could form 4, 8, 12, 16-port switch of RF and USB in order to test one specified devices from multiple DUTs.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"/Upload/ueditor/2018-03-02/1519971191.jpg\" title=\"1519971191.jpg\" alt=\"产品主图的尺寸.jpg\"/></p>','/2018-04-19/5ad802159ce12.jpg###/2018-04-19/5ad8021bd4e86.jpg###/2018-04-19/5ad8022136990.jpg','1524193578','admin',5,2,'UT-804 Magic Cube 1 to 4 RF and USB switch module','<dd>Control interface: Standard USB Type-A Female</dd>\r\n<dd>Working Voltege: +12V</dd>\r\n<dd>Working electric current: Max.3A</dd>\r\n<dd> Connection interface of DUT: USB Type-A Female *4 for USB 1.1/2.0</dd>\r\n<dd>System expansion interface: USB-Type-A Female*1</dd>\r\n<dd>RF interface: SMA Female*5</dd>','0.00',1,29,0,'<style>table {width:100%}\r\ntable tr td{text-align: left; font-family: \"微软雅黑\"; border-bottom: 0; border-right: 0; h